1
00:00:27,920 --> 00:00:29,039
Make sure you hide well.

2
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,559
Let's see if I can catch you.

3
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:54,119
Move.

4
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:31,400
Chen Hui actually rigged electric traps.

5
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,079
We'll settle all scores with him later.

6
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,560
There's something wrong with this bottle.

7
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:25,240
He just wants us dead.

8
00:02:27,439 --> 00:02:28,120
Damn it.

9
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,479
Could something have happened to Sun Bo?

10
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,120
Found it that easily?

11
00:03:08,719 --> 00:03:09,159
Captain Chu.

12
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:10,479
I found something.

13
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:19,280
What does a pig feed bag mean?

14
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:21,240
Anywhere in the city with surveillance,

15
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,479
Chen Hui couldn't possibly hide there.

16
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,840
So the clue

17
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,960
might be in this pig feed bag

18
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,080
and in this photo.

19
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:28,879
Captain Chu.

20
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,840
I'll have the techs analyze it now.

21
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:35,199
I just remembered.

22
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,120
This used to be a pig feed factory.

23
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,879
It was supposed to close down,

24
00:03:40,039 --> 00:03:41,879
but debt issues kept it from being demolished.

25
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,919
Yu Tianfang is hiding there.

26
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,400
I'll head over and meet you there now.

27
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:48,319
The address is...

28
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,800
Okay, I'll come pick you up.

29
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,039
Ma Xiaojun!

30
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,039
Sun Bo!

31
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:56,199
Sun Bo!

32
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:57,759
Sun Bo!

33
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,599
Sun Bo!

34
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:07,919
Sun Bo!

35
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:09,759
Sun Bo!

36
00:04:10,439 --> 00:04:11,560
What happened to Sun Bo?

37
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:24,439
Captain.

38
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:25,680
Mission...

39
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:28,040
accomplished.

40
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,240
Sun Bo!

41
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:31,800
Sun Bo!

42
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:47,720
Chu Feng, where are you going?

43
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,160
Where are you going?

44
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:50,439
To the feed factory.

45
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,680
To save Tianfang.

46
00:04:51,800 --> 00:04:52,680
I'll drive.

47
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:53,839
No need.

48
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:55,720
No need.

49
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,079
I know you blame yourself,

50
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,160
but all of this is Chen Hui's doing.

51
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,480
My father once said,

52
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:03,800
Chen Hui either checkmates,

53
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,800
or gets checkmated.

54
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:05,680
He's reckless and stubborn.

55
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:07,560
But we can't let emotions cloud us.

56
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,920
We have to stay rational.

57
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:11,600
Remember that saying?

58
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,720
Don't always focus on winning.

59
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,519
Watch the steps in front of you first.

60
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:21,600
This time,

61
00:05:22,240 --> 00:05:23,519
none of us has a way back.

62
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,920
But this game,

63
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:28,519
we have to win.

64
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,639
Hiding pretty well, kid.

65
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,560
Watch me find you.

66
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,279
You actually got away.

67
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:15,639
Hello?

68
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,399
Where are you?

69
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,360
He Siqi.

70
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,560
I'll give you a chance.

71
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:22,319
Yu Tianfang is in my hands.

72
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:24,319
Want to save his life? Come find me.

73
00:06:41,079 --> 00:06:41,680
Don't move!

74
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,879
I have a feeling Chen Hui

75
00:06:48,079 --> 00:06:49,240
has another scheme up his sleeve.

76
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,199
Besides us and Yu Tianfang,

77
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,720
the one Chen Hui hates most is He Siqi.

78
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:55,079
I have a bad feeling.

79
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:57,560
If Chen Hui has already contacted He Siqi,

80
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,160
He Siqi

81
00:06:59,759 --> 00:07:01,079
would probably sneak out.

82
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:25,759
He Siqi.

83
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,879
For that kid,

84
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:31,839
you don't even care about your own health.

85
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,279
Is he worth it?

86
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,680
Seeing you like this

87
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,079
breaks my heart.

88
00:07:36,279 --> 00:07:36,920
I'm here.

89
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,560
Let Yu Tianfang go.

90
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:40,360
I told you to come save Yu Tianfang,

91
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,839
but I never once mentioned

92
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:43,000
any conditions for releasing him.

93
00:07:43,079 --> 00:07:45,759
Because I never planned to escape from here.

94
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,839
So what do you have to bargain with?

95
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:50,040
What if I pay money to ransom him?

96
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,680
What money do you have?

97
00:07:53,079 --> 00:07:55,279
My mom left me lots of jewelry.

98
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,959
And every year on my birthday,

99
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:58,800
she'd give me a small gold bar.

100
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,079
In this case,

101
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,639
the gold bars alone weigh two pounds.

102
00:08:02,279 --> 00:08:03,079
I don't believe you.

103
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,560
The old you would never lie to me.

104
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,279
Everyone is selfish.

105
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:09,399
No matter how much I loved you,

106
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:11,560
I had to keep some security for myself.

107
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:12,759
After all,

108
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:14,639
the most appealing thing in this world

109
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,040
is money.

110
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:17,920
Open it up.

111
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,040
I want to see Yu Tianfang first.

112
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,399
What does that kid have that I don't?

113
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,199
You disgust me.

114
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:28,920
Let's go.

115
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:35,919
After you.

116
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,039
Siqi.

117
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:43,759
Siqi.

118
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,279
Tianfang.

119
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,240
Get out of here, now.

120
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,399
Don't worry about me.

121
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,039
Isn't this all because

122
00:08:51,639 --> 00:08:53,159
you want to drag someone down with you?

123
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:54,919
I'll trade myself for him.

124
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:56,240
Dying together with you

125
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:58,360
would be a fitting death, of course.

126
00:08:58,559 --> 00:08:59,080
But

127
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,240
this grudge between the three of us,

128
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:03,159
how could he not be present?

129
00:09:03,320 --> 00:09:04,960
Millions in jewelry and gold

130
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,600
are right inside this case.

131
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,480
Enough for you to flee.

132
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:09,919
Let him go.

133
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,360
What if I made you come with me

134
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,039
in exchange for his life?

135
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:16,039
Siqi.

136
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,600
Don't listen to him.

137
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,080
He's nothing but a cunning old fox.

138
00:09:20,679 --> 00:09:21,440
Don't worry.

139
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:24,039
I'd rather die than go with him.

140
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:26,080
Does our past mean nothing to you?

141
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,360
Being so heartless

142
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:28,759
really breaks my heart.

143
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:31,440
Women's hearts are the most venomous. Let me guess.

144
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,159
Inside this case of yours,

145
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:35,799
there might be some hidden trap or weapon.

146
00:09:35,799 --> 00:09:37,399
If I open it, I'll get hurt,

147
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:39,039
and the two of you can escape.

148
00:09:39,639 --> 00:09:41,080
I'm not as despicable as you.

149
00:09:51,799 --> 00:09:52,679
See?

150
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,759
I didn't lie to you.

151
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:55,639
Now let him go!

152
00:09:56,679 --> 00:09:57,480
Siqi.

153
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,879
You really underestimate me.

154
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,519
Do you really think

155
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,759
he's the only one I hate?

156
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,080
Siqi.

157
00:10:20,159 --> 00:10:20,960
What a thrill.

158
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:23,480
You almost set off the gas too early.

159
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,600
This move of yours,

160
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:26,120
the mask is off.

161
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:26,759
Fine.

162
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:28,159
It's my turn to play.

163
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:31,879
No!

164
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:34,600
Tianfang!

165
00:10:36,879 --> 00:10:37,600
Tianfang!

166
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:44,759
Tianfang!

167
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:46,480
Tianfang!

168
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:51,879
These genuine, heartfelt tears,

169
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:53,840
you've never shed any of them for me.

170
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,360
I really wonder

171
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,559
if you ever loved me at all.

172
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:00,600
Have you been treating me all along

173
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:02,840
as just a toy to pass the time?

174
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:03,759
That's right.

175
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,519
I was just playing you.

176
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,120
The one Siqi loves

177
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:10,120
has always been only me.

178
00:11:10,960 --> 00:11:13,399
You're not even worth a hair on my leg.

179
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:14,639
Shut up!

180
00:11:15,679 --> 00:11:16,960
Old and ugly,

181
00:11:17,879 --> 00:11:20,200
like a moldy old slab of cured meat.

182
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:22,320
Even a dog wouldn't touch it.

183
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,159
If I were you,

184
00:11:23,639 --> 00:11:25,159
I'd jump into a septic tank,

185
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:26,840
to spare society the pollution.

186
00:11:28,919 --> 00:11:29,480
Siqi.

187
00:11:37,120 --> 00:11:37,679
Tianfang!

188
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:38,759
If you've got the guts,

189
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,879
fight me one-on-one.

190
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:40,919
Let me go!

191
00:11:43,039 --> 00:11:44,080
Go to hell!

192
00:11:55,360 --> 00:11:56,480
The more you move,

193
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,279
the deeper the poison goes.

194
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,159
Beg me.

195
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:13,759
Beg me, and I'll give you a couple puffs.

196
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:24,159
I'd rather die than beg you.

197
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,320
Such backbone.

198
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:29,000
Then reflect carefully

199
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,799
on the wrongs you've done in this life.

200
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:31,600
And

201
00:12:31,799 --> 00:12:33,320
what regrets you've left unfulfilled.

202
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,480
The thing I regret most

203
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:40,039
is ever meeting you.

204
00:12:40,559 --> 00:12:41,759
The biggest mistake

205
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,600
was trusting you.

206
00:12:44,559 --> 00:12:45,799
What I regret most is

207
00:12:45,799 --> 00:12:47,399
not hacking you to death just now.

208
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:50,559
You're actually a pretty great girl.

209
00:12:51,200 --> 00:12:51,799
But

210
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:53,799
you didn't give all your love to me.

211
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:54,919
That's your fault.
